You okay, chief?

110
00:05:08,775 --> 00:05:10,660
You look a little
woozy there.

111
00:05:11,911 --> 00:05:14,414
Yeah.

112
00:05:14,449 --> 00:05:15,665
Yeah, i'm okay.

113
