Bridge, sonar.

124
00:05:58,574 --> 00:05:59,826
Bridge on.

125
00:05:59,861 --> 00:06:02,578
I have sonar contact
bearing 2-8-0 degrees

126
00:06:02,613 --> 00:06:03,830
