127
00:06:04,464 --> 00:06:06,332
Sounds like
a metal object.

128
00:06:12,088 --> 00:06:15,224
Bearing clear.

129
00:06:15,259 --> 00:06:17,093
What kind of
object, sonar?

130
00:06:17,128 --> 00:06:18,227
We can't tell, sir.

131
00:06:18,262 --> 00:06:20,730
From its appearance
on the scope,

132
00:06:20,765 --> 00:06:22,598
